Author: kastle_pro
Title: [ANN]üè∞ Kastle: Next Gen Cryptocurrency Exchange. [ICO] Whitelist Today: ‚úÖ
Body: Kastle Kastle is the next generation of cryptocurrency and digital asset exchange. Kastle is introducing utility tokens and digital assets to millions of users.   Problems   Demand for access to tokens continues to grow Listing process is not transparent Exchanges can't scale to meet consumer (use) or startup (list) demand New user registration closed at leading exchanges Exchanges charging over $1 million for token listing Projects can‚Äôt get listed on quality exchanges High risk & low quality exchanges fill demand Exchanges only offer features for traders not users  Solution   Build the next generation cryptocurrency exchange Enterprise grade performance, scale and security Cloud first and mobile first Transparent listing process Listing software to record & track startups onboarding -- like a mortgage application Simplified trading for users & mainstreet investors Investor research features based on information collected from listing software 3 month time to market  Features   Interface   Token Benefits   Akroma Kastle Token (AKT) will be a utility and rewards token for the Kastle exchange. The primary use for AKT will be to track a users` membership level, which is based on the amount of AKT held in your Kastle AKT wallet.  Level 1 10% off Trading Fees Required AKT: 10,000 Early Access & Beta Features  Level 2 20% off Trading Fees Required AKT: 20,000 Early Access & Beta Features  Level 3 40% off Trading Fees Required AKT: 40,000 Upgraded Support Trading fees can be paid in AKT Early Access & Beta Features  Level 4 80% off Trading Fees Required AKT: 80,000 Priority Support Trading fees can be paid in AKT Early Access & Beta Features  Token Distribution   Symbol: AKT Total Supply: 200,000,000 Technical Specification: ERC20 Decimals: 18 Network: Akroma  Distribution Token Sale: 50% Post-Launch Membership Sales: 35% Pre-Launch Marketing: 5 Advisors: 5% Pre-Sale Bonus: 5%  Token Sale   Token Sale Hard Cap: $10mm USD Token Price: $0.10 Whitelist Registration: Open! Token Sale Date: TBD Token Sale Time: 12:00PM GMT Sale Duration: 21 Days or once hard cap is reached Token Generation Event: 30 days from launch of Kastle and security audit of smart contract Can't Participate: CHINA, NORTH KOREA, SYRIA, USA KYC/AML/CTF: Any participant of the Kastle Token Sale will be required to identify themselves to meet minimum Anti-Money Laundering (AML), Counter-Terrorism Financing (CTF) and Know Your Customer (KYC) requirements.  Team   Advisors   Links Website |  Twitter  |  Discord  |  Telegram
